The PAV api is under devlopment and currently support the following url 
patterns. More to come.

Return type can either be infered by content negotiation (by setting request Accept header to 
desired content type) or by appending the content type to the url (.html, .xml, .json).

JsonP for cross-domain access is delivered to requests with callback param.

<ul>
